 />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:24:13.000Z","msg":"極左盟主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d92a56f17d5ecb2cf6a9580f2017b766d23de06","tid":2090351,"uid":82359,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"係極右滲透，定係極左搵藉口消滅想保家衛國嘅愛國右派呢？<br />\n<br />\n利申：陰毛論"},{"pid":"c165397a02517ce74c89f7ccd893db341119bd5b","tid":2090351,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"咩玩法 真解散定轉地下化"},{"pid":"368416294851f9394b48b1634ed72cadf61edcb2","tid":2090351,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:42:25.000Z","msg":"類似當年 革命黨滲透 湖北新軍"},{"pid":"2590562223b93ac8e6d3df53fc39333fb1ace9c2","tid":2090351,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"美軍走左 特種部隊又解散<br />\n德國武力真空??<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843fcba04712354d77928adfc9b8be87659c6f1a","tid":2090351,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2590562223b93ac8e6d3df53fc39333fb1ace9c2","tid":2090351,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"美軍走左 特種部隊又解散<br />\n德國武力真空??<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:27:48.000Z","msg":"добро пожаловать<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f473af347016eb182e6d687f607db77708aec2","tid":2090351,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T21:56:27.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n<br />\n搞到今時今日咁班友仲覺得係極右新納粹煽風點火，一隻手點拍得響，都唔諗下個套行左幾十年既多元文化主義係唔係真係仲行到落去好過啦，成個社會分成極左同極右咁你不如分裂成2個國家仲好啦，咁搞法遲早政變"}]}